duties_responsibilities.duty: Prepare, process, and move merchandise accurately and productively according to established guidelines, ensuring department standards are met.
Load and unload trailers, scan merchandise, build pallets, label merchandise, and sort and stock products.
Operate warehouse motor vehicles and hand and power equipment, adhering to safety procedures and performing basic math and computer operations.
Maintain neat and clean work area, follow safety guidelines, and work well with colleagues and supervisors.

education_certification.credential: High School Diploma or equivalent work experience
